WEBVTT

1
00:35:19.340 --> 00:35:22.400 
练习绕口令 锻炼舌头
and strengthen your tongue by repeating tongue twisters

2
00:35:22.430 --> 00:35:24.300 
比如说 四是四 十是十
For example, "I'm a thistle-sifter.

3
00:35:24.330 --> 00:35:25.860 
十四是十四
I have a sieve of sifted thistles and...

4
00:35:25.900 --> 00:35:28.840 
四十是四十
a sieve of unsifted thistles because I am a thistle-sifter.

5
00:35:28.870 --> 00:35:29.720 
行
Fine!

6
00:35:29.760 --> 00:35:31.890 
你的腹肌比较松软
You do have a flabby tummys,

7
00:35:31.930 --> 00:35:34.520 
我们要花时间增强你的横膈膜力量
we need spend some times to strength in your diaphragm.

8
00:35:34.550 --> 00:35:35.690 
很简单的物理治疗
Simple mechanics.

9
00:35:35.730 --> 00:35:36.800 
我们就需要这个
That is all we ask.

10
00:35:36.840 --> 00:35:38.010 
那我只收一先令就够了
And that's about a shilling's worth.

11
00:35:38.020 --> 00:35:40.520 
别提他妈的先令
Forget about the bloody shilling!

